<title>Tic‑Tac‑Pro — Play</title>
<style>
  body{margin:0;background:#0b0f1f;color:#e8ecff;font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;display:grid;min-height:100dvh;grid-template-rows:auto 1fr auto}
